        Constructs a new Cpe Object by parsing the vendor and product from the CPE identifier value.
        Parameters:
        value - the cpe identifier (cpe:/a:vendor:product:version:....)
        Throws:
        UnsupportedEncodingException - thrown if UTF-8 is not supported
